title: #1565 Electra Woman & Dyna Girl
itunes:title: #1565 Electra Woman & Dyna Girl
description:
Adam and Dr. Drew open the show with a discussion about Drew's mother's distaste for him and Adam recounts the similar distaste that his mother had, if not for him at least for everything he was interested in. They also explore Electra Woman and Dyna Girl as they do a deep dive into one of Sid & Marty Kroft's more obscure offerings. Thanks For Supporting Our Sponsors:
The Jordan Harbinger Show
